nodes.text: This Weequay lived in Mos Eisley on the Planet Tatooine and was an associate of the Rodian bounty hunter Greedo during the Clone Wars.

Around 21 BBY, this Weequay was found at Chalmun's Spaceport Cantina when Ion Papanoida and Chairman Notluwiski Papanoida along with Greedo came inside to recover the Chairman's kidnapped daughter. The Pantorans were undercover as agents of the Trade Federation so as not to raise the suspicion of the people inside the cantina, who were also involved in the kidnapping, yet once the Chairman's daughter had been brought forward, the identity of the Pantorans was revealed and this Weequay along with the gang of criminals inside started firing at them. During the firefight, this Weequay took cover behind the bar, but was eventually killed by Chairmon Papanoida.
